USAGE:

    <showTip (o) type="$TIP_TYPE"
             (o) color="$TEXT_COLOR"
             (o) duration="$TIP_DURATION">

             tip text....</showTip>


    $TIP_TYPE       - The display type of the tip:
                        0: Normal text
                        1: Jittering text

    $TEXT_COLOR     - The color of the displayed tip
    $TIP_DURATION   - How long the tip will last on screen in milliseconds

    e.g.
        <showTip color="YELLOW">Mission Complete!</showTip>